Package: containerd
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Recommends:
 containerd-tools (= ${binary:Version}),
 runc,
Description: Industry-standard container runtime (daemon)
 containerd is an industry-standard container runtime with an emphasis on
 simplicity, robustness, and portability. It is available as a daemon for
 Linux and Windows, which can manage the complete container lifecycle of its
 host system: image transfer and storage, container execution and supervision,
 low-level storage and network attachments, etc.
 .
 This package contains the containerd daemon and its runtime shim(s).

Package: containerd-tools
Architecture: any
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
Description: Industry-standard container runtime (client tools)
 containerd is an industry-standard container runtime with an emphasis on
 simplicity, robustness, and portability.
 .
 This package contains ctr, the low-level containerd CLI, and
 containerd-stress, the containerd stress-testing utility.
